{"tid":2274464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現時世界三大禍害: 伊斯蘭，共產黨，左膠","createTime":"2020-11-06T12:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T12:50:11.000Z","uid":318316,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8df4fb9db93b9c864199e1687d46de5941858e99","tid":2274464,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"劣幣驅逐良幣，  <br />\n可能人類社會文明就係畀啲三大禍害， 威脅住， <br />\n 如果佢哋勢力繼續蔓延， <br />\n對呢個世界嘅壞影響，真係不堪設想。"},{"pid":"bdaab6d50d631cc012f2c930664366b3e6be9db6","tid":2274464,"uid":60434,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"香港人最無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最適合做奴隸"},{"pid":"c37f26776864cc4a8467641d2dada9f8e7a63498","tid":2274464,"uid":77277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8df4fb9db93b9c864199e1687d46de5941858e99","tid":2274464,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"劣幣驅逐良幣，  <br />\n可能人類社會文明就係畀啲三大禍害， 威脅住， <br />\n 如果佢哋勢力繼續蔓延， <br />\n對呢個世界嘅壞影響，真係不堪設想。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:37:45.000Z","msg":"以上三樣野消失。個世界會美好好多"},{"pid":"48c9bca04c4877dafd97657cf003910207ca4bab","tid":2274464,"uid":210755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"共產黨成日將新疆維族人扣落isis<br />\n美左講穆斯林權益少數族裔人權 但新疆版圖都成百6萬平方公里,對佢地黎講好似唔存在咁"},{"pid":"d40a6dcd3ca4d5790146d3b0da1a8a82da03cd1d","tid":2274464,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"唯一對抗以上三樣野既人輸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後爽皮了 混亂既世界來臨了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bf1bf0f5bc6f6e68e74fa75be975169789feed","tid":2274464,"uid":370061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYeShCy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYeShCy.jpg&h=6edc3146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你了解伊斯蘭嗎？<br />\n<br />\n你去過阿拉伯嗎？<br />\n<br />\n知道伊朗從繁榮先進，幫助教徒走入貧困嗎？<br />\n<br />\n知道我們巴勒斯坦蛔蟲在以色列這個人均（GDP）36556美元的經濟體嗎有投票權嗎？<br />\n<br />\n知道我們把異教徒斬首強姦列入到可蘭經當中了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n你知道我們蛔蟲多聰明，只針對西方國家而對支那友好嗎？"},{"pid":"5810f0981ce7c59df738e8f9dcca147f168e4018","tid":2274464,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bdaab6d50d631cc012f2c930664366b3e6be9db6","tid":2274464,"uid":60434,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:36:29.000Z","msg":"香港人最無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最適合做奴隸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:49:07.000Z","msg":"事實又真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個女比人強姦都繼續開工"},{"pid":"878f28a9982693229e06182cdaa29ba99e1a90ec","tid":2274464,"uid":67815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"唔否認佢地存在有佢哋價值<br />\n正如當年奴隸制度廢除 都係靠呢班自由派既人<br />\n打破固有思維框架 令社會繼續進步<br />\n<br />\n但當然 自由歸自由<br />\n就好似解放奴隸制度 總有人會想推去更加極端<br />\n可能係要白人們永世賠償比一眾奴隸們<br />\n呢個時候就到保守派上場 拉番班人去正軌<br />\n以達至整個社會利益最大化<br />\n<br />\n而拉番正軌之前 人類總要食下屎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c6574c56d7fedc807a1810f7a58551c6f6fa88","tid":2274464,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><strong>[⇩ 民主左派 = 支共⇩]</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></p>"}]}